data.enText: sought
sought
to look for sth/sb

data.chText: 驾车者被告知需另寻其他路线。
data.enText: Drivers are advised to seek alternative routes.

data.chText: 他们怎么也找不到一个藏身的地方。
data.enText: They sought in vain for somewhere to shelter.
to try to obtain or achieve sth
to seek funding for a project

data.chText: 优秀秘书求职（广告用语）。
data.enText: Highly qualified secretary seeks employment. (= in an advertisement)

data.chText: 目前，我们正探索发展会员的新途径。
data.enText: We are currently seeking new ways of expanding our membership.
to ask sb for sth

data.chText: 我想我们现在该咨询一下律师了。
data.enText: I think it's time we sought legal advice.

data.chText: 她设法使他平静下来，然后向一位邻居求助。
data.enText: She managed to calm him down and seek help from a neighbour.
to try to do sth

data.chText: 他们迅速设法远离抗议者。
data.enText: They quickly sought to distance themselves from the protesters.

data.chText: 寻求（或追求）…的；对…的寻求（或追求）
data.enText: looking for or trying to get the thing mentioned; the activity of doing this

data.chText: 为引起他人的注意而作出的行为
data.enText: attention-seeking behaviour

data.chText: 参与义务工作有助于奠定求职的基础。
data.enText: Voluntary work can provide a framework for job-seeking.
seek your fortune

data.chText: 外出寻找发财机会；外出闯荡；闯世界
data.enText: to try to find a way to become rich, especially by going to another place
seek sb/sth out
to look for and find sb/sth, especially when this means using a lot of effort

ex.chText: 工会主席的职位急寻候选人。
ex.enText: Candidates are urgently sought for the post of trade union chairman.

ex.chText: 许多农村姑娘流入城市找工作。
ex.enText: Many country girls drifted into cities to seek work.

synonyms.bx: 语义庄重，语气较强，使用广泛，指尽很大努力去寻找合适的人或某种东西，此类东西多为抽象事物。

ex.chText: 警方搜遍全镇，力图找到凶手。
ex.enText: The police combed the whole town in their efforts to find the murderer.

ex.chText: 这所老房子被彻底搜查过了。
ex.enText: The old house was combed very carefully.

synonyms.bx: 表示对某处像梳头一般进行彻底搜寻。

ex.chText: 很多孩子在海滩上寻找贝壳。
ex.enText: Many kids were hunting for shells on the beach.
The police are busy hunting for clues.

synonyms.bx: 指非常仔细地寻找某人或某物，侧重于找的过程，通常后接介词 for。

ex.chText: 两个拿枪的士兵把他从头到脚搜了个遍。
ex.enText: Two soldiers with rifles searched him from head to foot.

ex.chText: 警察搜查了房子，什么也没有找到。
ex.enText: The policemen searched the house and found nothing.

ex.chText: 她弯腰在一大堆信件中翻找。
ex.enText: She bent to search through a heap of letters.

synonyms.bx: 指搜查某一具体的人、地方、事物以找到某物或某人，含非常仔细之意。

try to locate or discover, or try to establish the existence of
example: The police are searching for clues
They are searching for the missing man in the entire county
a liquid seeks its own level
He tried to shake off his fears
The infant had essayed a few wobbly steps
The police attempted to stop the thief
She always seeks to do good in the world

value.def: If you seek something such as a job or a place to live, you try to find one.

example.ex: They have had to seek work as labourers...
example.tran: 他们只好找体力活儿干。

example.ex: Four people who sought refuge in the Italian embassy have left voluntarily...
example.tran: 4 名在意大利大使馆寻求避难的人已经自愿离开了。

example.ex: Candidates are urgently sought for the post of Conservative party chairman.
example.tran: 保守党主席的职位急寻候选人。

value.def: When someone seeks something, they try to obtain it.

example.ex: The prosecutors have warned they will seek the death penalty...
example.tran: 检控方律师已警告说他们会努力争取判处死刑。

example.ex: Haemophiliacs are seeking compensation for being given contaminated blood.
example.tran: 血友病患者们因为被输入了受到污染的血液而正在寻求赔偿。

value.def: If you seek someone's help or advice, you contact them in order to ask for it.

example.ex: Always seek professional legal advice before entering into any agreement...
example.tran: 在签订任何协定之前一定要先征求法律专业人士的意见。

example.ex: On important issues, they seek a second opinion...
example.tran: 在重要问题上，他们会征求别人的看法。

example.ex: The couple have sought help from marriage guidance counsellors.
example.tran: 这对夫妇已经向婚姻指导顾问寻求帮助。

value.def: If you seek to do something, you try to do it.

example.ex: He also denied that he would seek to annex the country...
example.tran: 他还否认会试图吞并该国。

example.ex: Moscow is seeking to slow the growth of Russian inflation.
example.tran: 俄罗斯政府正力图遏制本国的通货膨胀。

trans: 追求；寻求；寻找,追求；探索；追寻
求助；寻求帮助；小三乞助；求救
